casebody.data:
No. 09-10553. Scott D. Johnson, Petitioner v. David A. Varano, Superintendent, State Correctional Institution at Coal Township, et al. 562 U.S. 802, 131 S. Ct. 89,

178 L. Ed. 2d 3,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 7832. October 4, 2010.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
